@startuml uc_08_functions
skinparam dpi 300
title UC08 - 函式呼叫

left to right direction
skinparam usecase {
  BackgroundColor white
  BorderColor black
  ActorBorderColor black
  FontSize 13
}

actor 開發者

rectangle "函式呼叫" {
  usecase "呼叫函式" as CALL
  usecase "呼叫使用者定義函式" as USER_FUNC
  usecase "呼叫內建函式" as BUILTIN
  usecase "傳遞引數" as ARGS
  usecase "查找函式定義" as LOOKUP_USER
  usecase "查找內建分派表" as LOOKUP_BUILTIN
  usecase "遞迴呼叫" as RECUR
}

開發者 --> CALL

CALL       ..> ARGS         : <<include>>
USER_FUNC  ..> LOOKUP_USER  : <<include>>
BUILTIN    ..> LOOKUP_BUILTIN : <<include>>
RECUR      ..> CALL         : <<extend>>\n{函式在本體內呼叫自身}

note right of RECUR : 條件: {函式在其本體內呼叫自身}\n延伸點: 函式呼叫自身

@enduml
